Type: Package
Package: openfulltext
Title: Functions to find open-access fulltext links and retrieve fulltext for academic papers
Version: 0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Lukas",
           family = "Wallrich",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "lukas.wallrich@gmail.com")
Description: retrieves fulltext links for academic papers from various sources based on DOIs, 
     and then also attempts to download the actual full text.
